<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Thu, 17 Aug 2023 21:05:39 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Tinder is losing the tool it uses for background checks]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Match Group 用来<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tinder-background-checks-garbo-165142514.html">为 Tinder 用户提供安全功能的</a>背景调查工具即将关​​闭。这家约会应用集团自 2019 年以来一直与女性创办的非营利性嘉宝公司合作，该公司将于 8 月底关闭其消费工具。 “大多数科技公司只是将信任和安全视为良好的公关，”嘉宝创始人兼首席执行官凯瑟琳·科斯米德斯 (Kathryn Kosmides) 告诉<em>《华尔街日报》</em> ，该报<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Wall Street Journal;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=2f007401-3eaa-4237-b69b-54ccbe125502&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Wall+Street+Journal&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdbWooq4NBQD1MCvNtUqA5pIRdpR7Dbn4O_s38Y4nfKe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ftech%2Ftinder-match-group-background-checks-nonprofit-end-46779f8b" class="rapid-with-clickid">发表了一份关于终止合作伙伴关系的报道</a>。 “我宁愿嘉宝将重点转移到我们的其他努力上，而不是让嘉宝的愿景受到损害并沦为大公司营销目标的一部分。”</p><p> Match Group 发言人向 Engadget 提供了一份声明。 “过去几年，Match Group 投入了大量资金来增强我们平台的安全性，我们将继续这样做。来自“你确定吗？”等功能和“这让你烦恼吗？”在背景调查方面，我们创建了其他约会应用程序无法提供的工具并进行了投资。我们致力于不断投资和构建行业领先的功能，为用户提供更多信息并控制他们选择在我们的平台上与谁联系。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该公司表示正在寻找替代合作伙伴来检查暴力历史。该发言人写道：“虽然我们对未能达成协议感到失望，但我们正在与替代提供商进行深入对话，并将很快宣布建立新的合作伙伴关系。” </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3daeda00-3d3e-11ee-bf3f-f4750caf9aab" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3daeda00-3d3e-11ee-bf3f-f4750caf9aab" style="height:3326px;width:5000px;" alt="中国 - 2023/02/19：在这张照片插图中，在线约会应用程序 Hinge 徽标显示在智能手机上，背景是经济证券交易所指数图。 （照片插图：Budrul Chukrut/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images）" data-uuid="6cc36a64-fc9c-3a70-876a-8ea2c605d7a9"><figcaption> Match Group 拥有和运营的约会应用程序包括 Hinge、Tinder、Match、OkCupid 和 Plenty of Fish（等等）。</figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> SOPA 图片来自 Getty Images</div></figure><p> Kosmides 告诉《<em>华尔街日报》</em> ，嘉宝决定暂停该工具是因为与 Match Group 存在分歧，以及难以让平台支付其服务费用。她描述了 Match Group 品牌内部关于如何使用该工具的争议。</p><p>据报道，Tinder 领导者推动建立一个系统，鼓励用户对自己进行背景调查，以便在他们的个人资料上获得徽章，该系统被描述为“一种吸引那些不太可能自行进行[背景调查]的人（主要是男性）的方式，并强调大多数人都是好人，” <em>《华尔街日报》</em>看到的一份内部文件写道。嘉宝拒绝了这个想法，科斯米德斯告诉该报，“你不能将某人列入白名单，也不能给他们一个‘好人，坏人’的身份验证。”</p><p> 2019 年， <em>ProPublica</em>发布了一篇<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/tinder-lets-known-sex-offenders-use-the-app-its-not-the-only-one">广为流传的关于性犯罪者使用约会应用程序的故事，</a>公众和监管机构对约会应用程序安全的兴趣有所上升。报道援引 Match Group 发言人的话说，“我们的免费产品中肯定存在登记的性犯罪者。”这场骚动导致国会山加大了审查力度。美国众议员 Jan Schakowsky（伊利诺伊州民主党）和 Ann Kuster（新罕布什尔州民主党）于 2020 年<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://schakowsky.house.gov/media/press-releases/schakowsky-kuster-lead-letter-match-group-president-calling-improvements">致函</a>Match Group，询问如何保护用户免受已登记的性犯罪者的侵害。两人于今年 7 月发出了一封后续信函，指出该约会公司不再披露其信任和安全团队的规模。</p><p>公众和政治兴趣的增强加大了 Match Group 采取行动的压力，据报道，其领导层将嘉宝（一种当时仍在开发中的未经测试的新产品）视为一种新颖的解决方案。这家约会集团于 2021 年<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tinder-match-group-garbo-background-check-data-142745236.html">宣布与该集团建立 150 万美元的合作伙伴关系</a>，并于次年推出了一款消费者工具——该公司付费为 Tinder 用户提供两次免费背景搜索服务。一些人批评此举提供了一种错误的安全感，尽管 Match Group 警告不要将其视为一种一体化解决方案。</p><p>今年夏天，由于 Match Group 和嘉宝未能就融资条款达成一致，后者的董事会召开会议并投票决定终止该工具。嘉宝也与规模较小的公司合作，表示将从 9 月 1 日开始恢复由志愿者运营。该组织<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.garbo.io/blog/%20next-phase-at-garbo">表示，</a>它将“将我们的努力重新集中在进一步的方法上，直接为个人提供新的和创新的工具，以保护自己免受数字时代基于性别的暴力和其他人际伤害。”</p><p>报告补充道，我们并没有放弃其核心使命，“我们还计划继续大力倡导刑事司法和公共记录系统的改革，以保护受害者并追究不良行为者的责任。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tinder-is-losing-the-tool-it-uses-for-background-checks-210539913.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tinder-is-losing-the-tool-it-uses-for-background-checks-210539913.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7abea2ad-62ec-4687-b705-84276bb7c896</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 21:05:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692306341</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T21:05:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Dating]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/033e2c40-1eee-11ee-b76f-fb683b2e39d8" width="6000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/033e2c40-1eee-11ee-b76f-fb683b2e39d8" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[In this photo illustration a Tinder logo seen displayed on a smartphone screen in Athens, Greece on May 5, 2023. (Photo illustration by Nikolas Kokovlis/NurPhoto via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Logo Photo Illustration]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Microsoft is holding a 'special event' on September 21st]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>夏季即将结束，这意味着科技活动的秋季繁忙季节即将到来。<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/microsoft/"><ins>微软</ins></a>已经通过向 9 月 21 日在纽约市举行的“特别活动”发出预约邀请来标记自己的领地，但该公司尚未提供任何有关预期活动的细节。</p><p>这很可能是微软秋季的重大硬件活动，在此期间该公司通常会展示其最新的 Surface 设备和其他设备。如果是这样，那就意味着微软在去年切换到<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-surface-2021-event-recap-185020522.html"><ins>10 月</ins></a><a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-surface-2022-event-live-blog-135459267.html"><ins>日期后，又回到了原来的 9 月末日期</ins></a>。无论如何，考虑到该公司过去一年左右的重点，它可能会在这次展示中大量谈论其各种人工智能方面的努力。我们总有机会了解 Windows 11 的新功能。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>科技行业的秋季日历正在形成。苹果通常会在 9 月初至中旬展示其最新款 iPhone（今年可能会或可能不会配备<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-pro-set-to-feature-a-thinner-bezel-titanium-frame-and-usb-c-charging-094118389.html">USB-C 充电端口</a>），但尚未确认具体日期。谷歌也没有，它肯定会在未来一两个月的某个时候发布其新的 Pixel 设备。亚马逊将于<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.thurrott.com/amazon/285395/amazon-teases-hardware-event-september-20"><ins>9 月 20 日</ins></a>举办一场硬件活动，比微软的活动早一天。同时，我们将于<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-connect-2023-event-is-set-for-september-27th-154545337.html"><ins>9 月 27 日</ins></a>在 Meta Connect 上了解有关<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-meta-quest-3-is-a-499-mixed-reality-headset-with-full-color-passthrough-141204527.html?src=rss">Meta Quest 3 的</a>更多信息。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-is-holding-a-special-event-on-september-21st-194223173.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-is-holding-a-special-event-on-september-21st-194223173.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 204d5791-2f48-4386-84ea-cb92dc7c5c42</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 19:42:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692301344</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T19:42:29+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="456" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/51f2c610-3d35-11ee-a5ef-ee0f3d5fb81a" width="859"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="456" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/51f2c610-3d35-11ee-a5ef-ee0f3d5fb81a" width="859"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Microsoft]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Microsoft September 2023 event logo, featuring splotches of red, greed, yellow and blue around four white squares.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Microsoft September 2023 event logo]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[X may soon add ID verification for 'preventing impersonation']]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在猖獗的冒充行为暂时<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-blue-verification-impersonation-disaster-203656712.html"><ins>破坏了</ins></a>该公司的付费验证计划几个月后，X 似乎正在开发新的身份验证功能。根据应用程序研究员 Nima Owji<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/nima_owji/status/1691850092385370483"><ins>分享的</ins></a>屏幕截图，该平台目前正在开发一项额外的验证功能，要求用户上传政府颁发的身份证件副本并拍摄自拍照。</p><p> Owji 经常发现 X 中未发布的功能，本月早些时候，他首次在马斯克的个人资料中发现了“身份验证”徽章。现在，他发现了一条应用程序内消息，详细说明了它的工作原理，这表明它可能距离正式发布越来越近了。 “通过提供政府颁发的身份证件来验证您的帐户，”它说。 “这通常需要大约 5 分钟。”它解释说，用户需要提供身份证件照片和自拍照。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="02db3b646e304e8aa7901be3cf483ead"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/X?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#X</a>继续进行身份验证。您应该上传身份证件照片并拍摄实时自拍照。 <a href="https://t.co/3bdGgzlnZh">https://t.co/3bdGgzlnZh</a> <a href="https://t.co/F4ssglakHR">pic.twitter.com/F4ssglakHR</a></p> — 尼玛·奥吉 (@nima_owji) <a href="https://twitter.com/nima_owji/status/1691850092385370483?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 16 日</a></blockquote></div><p>X 似乎正在与第三方“身份智能”公司 Au10tix 合作开发该功能。细则指出，为了验证而共享的信息将被 Au10tix 以及 X 看到。X 将保留“包括生物识别数据在内的身份证图像长达 30 天”，并将使用这些信息“用于安全和安保的目的，包括防止冒充。”</p><p> Au10tix 的代表没有立即回应置评请求。该公司的网站<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.au10tix.com/company/about/"><ins>宣传</ins></a>“8秒验证，甚至无需部分人工参与”和“全球首创的检测合成欺诈模式的技术”。该公司表示，此前曾与谷歌、PayPal 和 Uber 等公司合作。</p><p> X 没有回应置评请求。但该功能表明该公司正在寻找新的方法来打击平台上的假冒行为。目前，X 向任何支付 X Premium（以前称为 Twitter Blue）订阅费用的人提供经过验证的状态。</p><p>该公司并不进行自己的身份检查，尽管它已经实施了一些保障措施，例如其<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitter-early-access-waitlist-organization-verification-093816293.html"><ins>经过验证的组织</ins></a>功能。尽管如此，一些冒充者仍然成功<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://mashable.com/article/disney-junior-fake-account-twitter-verified"><ins>逃脱</ins></a>。验证也被<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://protos.com/twitter-verification-is-making-scammers-millions-heres-how/"><ins>许多诈骗者</ins></a>利用，特别是加密货币诈骗者，他们利用 X 高级订阅附带的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitters-video-and-ranking-perks-arrive-to-paying-blue-subscribers-125538009.html"><ins>额外可见性</ins></a>来提升他们的帖子。目前尚不清楚添加可选的身份检查是否可以完全解决这些问题，但它可能会使一些诈骗者和冒充者更容易识别。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/x-may-soon-add-id-verification-for-preventing-impersonation-190422905.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/x-may-soon-add-id-verification-for-preventing-impersonation-190422905.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> aae895b6-58fb-4ec9-ac3f-3ddd93e36e4b</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 19:04:22 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692299063</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T19:04:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3aea1d10-3d30-11ee-be95-bb8fea41f481" width="6000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3aea1d10-3d30-11ee-be95-bb8fea41f481" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Clodagh Kilcoyne / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The new logo of Twitter is displayed on an iPhone in Galway, Ireland July 24, 2023. REUTERS/Clodagh Kilcoyne]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[TWITTER-MUSK/LOGO]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Homeworld: Deserts of Kharak’ will be free on the Epic Games Store this month]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <em>《家园：卡拉克沙漠》</em>将于本月晚些时候在 Epic Games Store 上免费提供。 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-09-13-gaming-irl-control-wow-classic.html">广受好评的</a>1999 年即时战略经典<em>《家园》</em>前传于 2016 年推出，先于<em>《家园 3》</em>在<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/homeworld-3-delay-gearbox-interactive-blackbird-rts-165808680.html">多次推迟</a>后于<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sci-fi-strategy-game-homeworld-3-has-been-delayed-to-february-2024-061237843.html">明年初</a>推出。<em>卡拉克沙漠</em>（通常价值 50 美元）将于 8 月 24 日至 31 日在 Epic 店面领取。</p><p> 2016 年的游戏发生在<em>家园</em>事件发生一个多世纪之前，发生在卡拉克沙漠世界。这颗干旱的星球是贵霜人曾经的家园，他们是该系列 1999 年原著和核心人物的主角。这是唯一一款将动作从太空转移到地面的《家园》游戏，你可以在地形中导航，以获得对加奥基斯的优势。这个类似邪教的派系认为，任何梦想飞向星空的人都应该受到严厉的惩罚——而他们却乐于接受这种惩罚。它的游戏玩法尊重该系列的战略根源，同时通过将海拔（穿越沙漠的高原和山谷）作为核心焦点来适应地面游戏减少的运动轴。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>免费抢到这款游戏可以让该系列的粉丝们在 2024 年 2 月推出<em>《家园 3》</em>之前渡过难关——而发行商 Gearbox Software 肯定会很乐意吸引一些年轻玩家加入这个拥有近 25 年历史的系列游戏。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/21e085e0-3d29-11ee-957f-3e20f951af42" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/21e085e0-3d29-11ee-957f-3e20f951af42" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="《家园：卡拉克沙漠》的宣传剧照。一辆带有 U 形炮塔的红色坦克向远处的敌人发射火焰。沙漠环境，2016 PC 游戏图形。" data-uuid="60ea62fd-0ed9-356d-b461-c82c105e9c10"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">变速箱软件</div></figure><p>自 RTS 类型的 90 年代末 00 年代初鼎盛时期以来，《家园》系列就经历了 IP 过山车般的发展。在第一款游戏广受好评后，原始开发商 Relic Entertainment 又制作了两款（也广受好评）游戏：扩展包和续集。然而，在2003年的<em>《家园2》</em>之后，THQ收购了Relic，但未能在其旗下制作任何一款《家园》游戏。</p><p>在 THQ 倒闭、Gearbox Software 赢得 2013 年拍卖以确保其权利后，该系列才再次获得新生。 《无主之地》的制作者通过经典作品的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2015-02-24-homeworld-remastered-review.html">重制版</a>重新演绎了这个传奇故事。不久之后， <em>《卡拉克沙漠》也</em>随之推出， <em>《家园 3》</em>最终于 2019 年发布，通过众筹活动筹集资金并衡量消费者的兴趣。经过几次推迟后，期待已久的第三部分（希望）将于明年冬天到达。</p><p>领取 8 月 24 日至 31 日期间的 PC 游戏需要 Epic Games 帐户。在此期间，您可以在浏览器中导航至<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/homeworld-deserts-of-kharak"><em>Deserts of Kharak 商店页面</em></a>或使用 Epic Games Launcher 进行兑换。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/homeworld-deserts-of-kharak-will-be-free-on-the-epic-games-store-this-month-181511485.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/homeworld-deserts-of-kharak-will-be-free-on-the-epic-games-store-this-month-181511485.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3a4c129d-4d01-494b-adf1-2110d8fd1f00</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 18:15:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692297903</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T18:45:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/278b0d60-3d26-11ee-bde4-0ae67aa0a6db" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/278b0d60-3d26-11ee-bde4-0ae67aa0a6db" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Gearbox Software]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Gameplay screen from the 2016 real-time strategy game ‘Homeworld: Deserts of Kharak.’ A red carrier is surrounded by red assault vehicles in a desert climate. 2016 PC video game graphics.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Homeworld: Deserts of Kharak]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA['Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III' will include the series' biggest zombies map ever]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>动视暴雪透露了有关<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-next-call-of-duty-game-is-modern-warfare-iii-165748261.html"><em>《使命召唤：现代战争 III》的秘密，</em></a>透露了更多有关玩家对重启系列的下一款作品的期待。一方面，《使命召唤》 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-vanguard-zombies-trailer-170042898.html">僵尸模式</a>的粉丝们似乎正在享受一场盛宴。动视承诺将推出该模式迄今为止最大的地图。你将能够第一次与其他小队组队，并尝试在“大群”僵尸中生存。</p><p>尽管 Sledgehammer Games 主导了<em>《现代战争 III》的开发，但</em>许多其他动视工作室也提供了帮助。 Treyarch 是《使命召唤》的核心开发者之一，负责今年的僵尸模式，该模式讲述了一个“黑暗以太”的故事。动视表示，除了需要揭开的秘密和各种需要检查的任务外，《僵尸》还包括“开放世界的 PvE 撤离生存体验”以及该系列历史上一些最大的敌人。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="0f781da19ac542a5b87f9c7ae92626ba"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mHDEDDrGYvo?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p>当然，《僵尸》并不是唯一的主要多人游戏模式， <em>《MWIII》</em>将向该系列的最高点之一致敬。 2009 年版<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-03-31-call-of-duty-modern-warfare-2-campaign-remastered-now-available-ps4.html"><em>《现代战争 2》</em></a>中最初的 16 张多人游戏地图中的每一张都将从一开始就可供使用。 Sledgehammer 对 Terminal 和 Highrise 等经典地图进行了现代化改造，并提供了新的模式和游戏功能。未来赛季将推出超过 12 张新的六对六地图。</p><p>从一开始，就会出现三张新的战斗地图，您可以在地面战争和入侵模式中一决胜负，还有一张战争地图。后者标志着战争模式的回归，该模式在 2017 年的<em>《使命召唤：WWll》</em>中让该系列退出。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/de316f10-3d25-11ee-97de-b93fff20ed29" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/de316f10-3d25-11ee-97de-b93fff20ed29" style="height:2160px;width:3840px;" alt="在《使命召唤：现代战争 III》的多人游戏模式中，士兵们躲在盾牌后面。" data-uuid="32c6334c-321c-3f66-9af3-1c315e2d8982"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">大锤游戏/动视</div></figure><p>您可以期待新的移动机制，例如用于战术近距离战斗的战术姿态。动视表示，Sledgehammer 改进了重新装填取消和滑动取消机制，同时你应该会发现它可以更快地瞄准滑动之外的瞄准器。与此同时，所有福利都将在多人比赛开始时提供，包括一种名为隐蔽运动鞋的新无声运动。</p><p>许多玩家会很高兴地得知，继 Infinity Ward 在去年的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mwii-modern-warfare-ii-warzone-2-no-russian-170044023.html"><em>《现代战争 II》</em></a>中省略了经典的红点小地图之后，它又回来了。将会有一个地图投票系统，而《大锤》给玩家带来了健康提升，这将增加击杀时间——我相信玩家不会对这一变化有任何意见。</p><p>您不必从头开始收集多人游戏装备。上周， <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-players-can-bring-most-of-their-modern-warfare-ii-gear-over-to-modern-warfare-iii-170024613.html">动视暴雪确认</a>，玩家将能够将几乎所有已解锁的物品（包括武器和操作员）从<em>《现代战争 II》</em>转移到<em>《现代战争 III》。</em> </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/01e21770-3d26-11ee-adf5-bb3cc77eeac7" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/01e21770-3d26-11ee-adf5-bb3cc77eeac7" style="height:2160px;width:3840px;" alt="在《使命召唤：现代战争 III》的战役模式中，一名士兵走过树林。" data-uuid="6e1a464a-3613-3b8b-9ae3-d1cf97755e6b"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">大锤游戏/动视</div></figure><p>除了所有多人游戏功能之外，还有战役的小问题。这是去年游戏的直接续作，延续了《现代战争》的故事，特遣部队 141 试图打倒极端民族主义恶棍弗拉德米尔·马卡洛夫。这一次，出现了一种名为“公开战斗”的新型任务。这为玩家提供了选择自己的关卡路径的机会，并且他们将有多种方法来完成目标。这些关卡是根据玩家偏好的游戏风格而构建的，因此，如果您更喜欢隐秘的方式而不是全枪扫射的方式，您可能会欣赏它们的灵活性。</p><p>动视暴雪还发布了一个新的游戏预告片，这支持了人们的猜测，即原版<em>《现代战争 2》</em>中备受争议的“禁止俄罗斯人”任务将会有新的呈现。当收件人在飞机上行走时，在用枪指着之前，短信中会出现“禁止俄语”的字样。</p><p> <em>《使命召唤：现代战争 III》</em>将于 11 月 10 日登陆 PS4、PS5、Xbox One、Xbox Series X/S 和 PC（通过 Steam 和 Battle.net）。事先将有一个免费的公开测试版，预购者可以抢先体验。这些人还可以在游戏正式发布日期前一周玩该活动。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-iii-will-include-the-series-biggest-zombies-map-ever-180029216.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-iii-will-include-the-series-biggest-zombies-map-ever-180029216.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 84de5f97-6c4f-45e2-99d7-35225f5274cc</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 18:00:29 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692295947</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T18:12:32+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/afc87ba0-3d25-11ee-bfff-85b408ee931b" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/afc87ba0-3d25-11ee-bfff-85b408ee931b" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Sledgehammer Games/Treyarch/Actvision]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A giant mutated enemy and some humanoid zombies in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III's Zombies mode.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III's Zombies mode]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best VR headsets for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您一直在等待 VR 硬件成熟，那么您的选择是明智的。自六年前推出 Oculus Rift 和 HTC Vive 以来，耳机已经取得了长足的进步。 Meta Quest 2 已经问世两年了，事实证明它是一种非常强大的便携式 VR 体验。如果您正在寻找更实用、更身临其境的体验，高端 PC 耳机正变得越来越便宜，并且在主要零售商中越来越广泛地销售。虽然自去年以来整个 VR 市场并没有发生太大变化（除了有点令人失望的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-quest-pro-review-a-next-gen-headset-for-the-vr-faithful-specs-price-130045313.html">Meta Quest Pro</a> ），但至少有很多 VR 体验值得深入研究。</p><h2><br>那么什么才是一款好的 VR 耳机呢？</h2><p>我倾向于根据一些基本标准来判断虚拟现实耳机：人体工程学、沉浸感和控制。将移动显示器塞进塑料耳机并在其上绑上一些廉价的弹性头带并不难。但需要技巧才能制作出非常平衡且 30 分钟后不会感到不舒服的东西。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>与此同时，沉浸感来自于具有快速刷新率的高分辨率屏幕，因此视觉效果清晰流畅。视场 (FOV) 也是一个主要元素，因为它描述了 VR 屏幕能否很好地覆盖您在游戏中看到的内容。视野较低会让您感觉像是在通过双筒望远镜观看，这限制了您的“存在感”。最好的 VR 耳机拥有广阔的视野，让您仿佛真的在 Google 地球中飞越地球。</p><p>当谈到控制器时，最好的选择自然适合您的手中并提供准确的跟踪。业界基本上采用了 Meta 出色的触摸控制器的设计，但我们也看到了一些有趣的飞跃，例如 Valve 的手指追踪游戏手柄。</p><p></p><h2>最适合大多数人的 VR 耳机：Meta Quest 2</h2><p><core-commerce id="d84530e04e7a469d8dc7b5a48f2fafe6" data-type="product-list"></p><p>自发布两年多以来， <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9PY3VsdXMtUXVlc3QtQWR2YW5jZWQtQWxsLU9uZS1WaXJ0dWFsL2RwL0IwOTlWTVQ4Vlo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZGMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg1ZmYzNGJmLWY2ZjctNDg3OC04MGMxLTVmMTU1ZTdhZjE0YiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQFeq6Fas1jV9ohaGomag8_kstKpjjQIA8yViHmVHwnB&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOculus-Quest-Advanced-All-One-Virtual%2Fdp%2FB099VMT8VZ">Meta Quest 2</a> （以前称为 Oculus Quest 2）仍然是绝大多数消费者的最佳 VR 耳机。它完全无线，长时间佩戴也很舒适。不幸的是，由于供应链压力和日益恶化的经济环境，Meta 今年最终将 Quest 2 的价格提高了 100 美元，使其成为一款 400 美元的耳机。它仍然是一个很棒的设备，但它也处于一个奇怪的位置，比去年更糟糕。</p><p>不过，这仍然是好的：有一个巨大的虚拟现实游戏库，您可以在任何地方体验，并且它与 Meta 出色的运动感应控制器捆绑在一起。您还可以将 Quest 2 连接到游戏 PC 以串流更复杂的 VR 体验。</p><p> Quest 2 采用快速切换 LCD，每眼显示分辨率为 1832x1920，这是我们在 Meta 上看到的最高分辨率。它还具有平滑的 90Hz 刷新率，这对于完全在移动硬件上运行的东西来说令人印象深刻。 Quest 2 的视野不是最好的——测量时只有 90 度左右——但仍然足以享受大多数 VR 体验。您还可以<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.vrfitnessinsider.com/i-boosted-my-quest-2s-field-of-view-halfway-to-a-valve-index-vrcover-foam-pads-fov-rated/">使用不同的面罩</a>来稍微增加其视野。如果您想要更舒适的佩戴体验，您可以花<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9PY3VsdXMtUXVlc3QtRWxpdGUtRW5oYW5jZWQtU3VwcG9ydC1Db21mb3J0L2RwL0IwOEY1VFpXMko_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZGMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg1ZmYzNGJmLWY2ZjctNDg3OC04MGMxLTVmMTU1ZTdhZjE0YiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXrou7_GB6xZ3P8AxaWDvGKaejSoZm_fBfIBci16MH7t&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOculus-Quest-Elite-Enhanced-Support-Comfort%2Fdp%2FB08F5TZW2J">49 美元购买 Elite 头带</a>（或<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9PY3VsdXMtQmF0dGVyeS1DYXJyeWluZy1FbmhhbmNlZC1Db21mb3J0LVBsYXl0aW1lL2RwL0IwOEY1VDNGOVk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZGMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijg1ZmYzNGJmLWY2ZjctNDg3OC04MGMxLTVmMTU1ZTdhZjE0YiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdDaXGYjY6UVied7C83ADzuZ-s5Xve5pAtq3US3A3IiY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOculus-Battery-Carrying-Enhanced-Comfort-Playtime%2Fdp%2FB08F5T3F9Y">129 美元，带内置电池和充电盒</a>）。</p><p> Meta <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/quest-2-foam-facial-interface-recall-163432642.html#:~:text=Working%20with%20the%20US%20Consumer,with%20its%20latest%20VR%20headset.&amp;text=Facebook%20is%20also%20halting%20sales,to%20every%20Quest%202%20package.">召回了原型号的泡沫衬垫</a>，并提供硅胶套，以使耳机更加舒适。在我们的审查期间或在过去一年的使用过程中，我们没有遇到任何问题，但已经有足够多的投诉让 Facebook 采取行动。售价 399 美元的 Quest 2 还配备 128GB 存储空间，是原始型号的两倍，为您提供更多空间来塞入 VR 游戏和应用程序。</p><p> Quest 2 可能无法提供最佳的整体 VR 体验，但它无疑是市场上最方便使用的耳机。 （至少在我们明年可能看到后续行动之前。）</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/oculus-quest-2-review-vr-facebook-headset-173026291.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Meta Quest 2 VR 耳机的完整评论</strong></a></p><p></p><h2>最佳 VR 主机：PlayStation VR2</h2><p><core-commerce id="012b544e165942b5b9f134356312ed44" data-type="product-list"></p><p>从很多方面来说， <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RpcmVjdC5wbGF5c3RhdGlvbi5jb20vZW4tdXMvY29uc29sZXMvY29uc29sZS9wbGF5c3RhdGlvbnZyMi4xMDAwMDMzNTc5IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4NWZmMzRiZi1mNmY3LTQ4NzgtODBjMS01ZjE1NWU3YWYxNGIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAASVFmJQbMlkTyWMH_ugyvJSC_foJ9_i4O_hUdGlQu5zT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fdirect.playstation.com%2Fen-us%2Fconsoles%2Fconsole%2Fplaystationvr2.1000033579">PS VR2</a>都是我们测试过的最好的耳机。它提供双 2K OLED HDR 屏幕，有效为您提供 4K 画质和身临其境的 VR 体验。它是目前<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playstation-vr2-review-great-headset-should-be-cheaper-130032254.html">最舒适的耳机之一</a>。它具有一些真正令人耳目一新的新功能，例如眼球追踪和耳机触觉。 （是的，它确实可以震撼您的头脑。）最重要的是，PS VR2 可以提供高质量的虚拟现实，而无需 1,000 美元以上的游戏 PC - 您只需要一台 PlayStation 5。</p><p>现在，我们的建议带有一些注意事项。 PS VR2 的售价为 550 美元，比 PS5 本身还要贵。目前尚不清楚其游戏库将多快填满（最初的运行只有一些独占游戏，例如<em>《Horizo​​n VR》</em>和<em>《Gran Turismo 7</em> 》）。但这是体验高端 VR 的最简单方式，而且是对原始 PS VR 的重大升级。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playstation-vr2-review-great-headset-should-be-cheaper-130032254.html"><strong>阅读我们对 PlayStation VR2 耳机的完整评论</strong></a></p><p></p><h2>600 美元以下最佳 PC VR 耳机：HP Reverb G2</h2><p><core-commerce id="f138dcf2cf174d5f83de93effb029303" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您不关心无线 VR，并且想在高品质 PC 虚拟现实耳机上投入更多， <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAU8yuwb4LPkC9aq-FwtzTfc5m5cydhv9-Jh3N1rWGM-5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHeadset-Controller-Adjustable-Speakers-Ergonomic-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB08TB5J7KY">那么 HP 599 美元的 Reverb G2</a>非常适合您。它是与 Valve 合作开发的，具有价格较高的 Index 耳机的一些最佳功能，例如近场扬声器。 Reverb G2 还拥有清晰的屏幕，每眼提供 2,160 x 2,160 像素、90Hz 刷新率和相对较宽的 114 度视野。</p><p>它也是第一款包含四个传感器的 Windows 混合现实耳机，有助于确保更准确的 VR 跟踪功能，尤其是在快节奏的游戏中。我还赞扬惠普制造了一款系留 VR 耳机，由于目镜和后带周围有豪华的缓冲垫，该耳机非常舒适。</p><p> Reverb G2 的运动控制器不是我最喜欢的，但它们仍然比 HP 之前的型号有了很大的进步。您还可以升级它以使用 Valve 的手指跟踪控制器，但这涉及到 SteamVR 传感器和更多设置。不过，有可用的升级路径还是很高兴的。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hp-reverb-g2-review-vr-windows-mixed-reality-130012057.html"><strong>阅读我们对 HP Reverb G2 VR 耳机的完整评论</strong></a></p><p></p><h2>最适合游戏玩家的 PC VR 耳机：Valve Index</h2><p><core-commerce id="ed91317a851b4674bcc479fdd2036c43" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N0b3JlLnN0ZWFtcG93ZXJlZC5jb20vdmFsdmVpbmRleCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiODVmZjM0YmYtZjZmNy00ODc4LTgwYzEtNWYxNTVlN2FmMTRiIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAcYko-dGLUFMrsz46tO6ABx3AQAUIaUCK3XdQLrlVQym&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fvalveindex">Valve 的 Index 套件</a>仍然是 PC 游戏市场上最好的高端 VR 解决方案之一。只需 999 美元，您就可以获得 Index 耳机、Valve 的手指跟踪控制器和两个 SteamVR 基站。虽然我们在过去两年中看到了更高分辨率的耳机，但它仍然是一个非常可靠的选择，具有 1,440 x 1,600 像素分辨率、令人眼花缭乱的 144Hz 刷新率和巨大的 130 度视野。我很乐意失去一些像素来获得更平滑、更广阔的屏幕，这仍然远远超出任何其他消费类耳机。</p><p>作为一款 SteamVR 产品，Index 需要在房间的相对角落安装两个传感器。当然，它是连接到您的电脑的。但为了更高的刷新率和更准确的跟踪，这种笨拙是值得的。当然，它不像 Quest 2 那么容易使用，但在这个价格范围内，我们假设您在获得真正高质量的 VR 游戏体验时会遇到一些不便。</p><p> Valve 的手指追踪控制器也非常棒，有一条方便的带子可以将它们锁定在你的手上。他们让玩<em>《半衰期：爱莉克斯》</em>感觉就像一场梦。不幸的是，其他 VR 游戏还没有充分利用手指追踪功能。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-06-28-valve-index-review-vr.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Valve Index VR 套件的完整评论</strong></a></p><p></p><h2>无论成本如何，最佳 VR 质量：HTC Vive Pro 2</h2><p><core-commerce id="4efd19a6db194005a4bf6d0ee71fb5d3" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlGUENUM0g4Lz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby1kYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiODVmZjM0YmYtZjZmNy00ODc4LTgwYzEtNWYxNTVlN2FmMTRiIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAbIfFJwh94FAXF8dh3EuNAtYS0hhu_zdCTW83DVKM95B&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09FPCT3H8%2F">HTC 的 Vive Pro 2</a>是我见过的最好看的 PC VR。它拥有令人惊叹的锐利 5K 屏幕和稳定的 120Hz 刷新率。请做好准备：全套套件包括耳机、两个 SteamVR 传感器和魔杖控制器，售价 1,399 美元。您还可以<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDkyTEJMVDdQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWRjLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4NWZmMzRiZi1mNmY3LTQ4NzgtODBjMS01ZjE1NWU3YWYxNGIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAdAjnazZa_KrRPeknPmuBX9SeTcsMMUTGi-T8vd_GTy0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB092LBLT7P">花费 799 美元购买独立耳机，</a>作为原始 Vive Pro 或 Valve Index 的升级。</p><p>您可以以同样的价格获得一款平衡性良好且极其舒适的 VR 耳机。 <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/htc-vive-pro-2-review-5k-vr-headset-133100685.html#:~:text=The%20HTC%20Vive%20Pro%202,make%20it%20a%20tough%20sell.">Pro 2</a>清楚地表明 Valve 已经几乎完善了高端硬件的制造艺术。我对大型魔杖控制器印象不太深刻，它们与 2016 年初代 HTC Vive 附带的控制器一模一样。它们很实用，但远不如 Oculus 的触摸控制器那么符合人体工程学。</p><p>我在这里主要推荐Pro 2，因为它的耳机质量令人惊叹。</p><p>真正的 VR 粉丝可能只想单独购买 SteamVR 基站和 Valve 的手指追踪控制器。这样您就可以确保您在玩<em>手枪鞭子</em>时获得最佳体验。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/htc-vive-pro-2-review-5k-vr-headset-133100685.html"><strong>阅读我们对 HTC Vive Pro 2 VR 耳机的完整评论</strong></a></p><p></p><h2>常见问题解答</h2><h3>VR头显如何工作？</h3><p>从最基本的层面来说，VR 耳机只是一个贴在脸上的高质量屏幕。对于有线耳机，渲染游戏的实际工作是在 PC 或游戏机上完成的。对于完全无线的设备，例如 Meta Quest 2，该工作直接在耳机上处理。它们依靠外部传感器或耳机内置的传感器来绘制您的物理空间。虽然您可以在 VR 中使用传统的游戏手柄或键盘和鼠标，但他们通常使用运动跟踪控制器来让您沉浸在 3D 环境中。</p><h3>哪种 VR 耳机最适合全身追踪？</h3><p>虽然我们仍在等待真正出色的触觉 VR 连体衣的到来，但您仍然可以使用大多数与 Steam VR 兼容的 PC 耳机实现准确的身体跟踪。 Valve Index 和 HTC Vive Pro 2 都依赖于房间跟踪传感器，与竞争对手的内置传感器相比，这些传感器可以更有效地绘制您的身体图。您还可以将 HTC Vive 追踪器添加到腕带、腿带以及腰带上，以获得更好的覆盖范围。 Meta Quest 2 没有任何简单的身体跟踪解决方案，但您可以<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.vr-wave.store/blogs/virtual-reality-prescription-lenses/get-full-body-tracking-on-your-quest-2">在将其插入 PC 时添加 Vive 跟踪器</a>以模仿 Steam VR 耳机。</p><p>目前只有少数体验（例如 VRChat）利用全身跟踪。目前，PlayStation VR 和 VR2 还没有任何人体跟踪解决方案，但我们对该公司的<a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.vr-wave.store/blogs/virtual-reality-prescription-lenses/get-full-body-tracking-on-your-quest-2">Mocopi 人体跟踪器</a>很感兴趣，该产品确实是在日本发布的。</p><h3>哪些 VR 耳机比 Oculus 更好？</h3><p> Oculus 是 Meta 的 VR 硬件的旧称。目前，该公司仅支持 Meta Quest 2 和 Quest Pro，这两款耳机都是无线耳机。正如我们上面所解释的，PC VR 耳机通常可以实现更好质量的虚拟现实，因为它们依赖于更强大的图形硬件。</p><h3>哪些 VR 耳机可与 Xbox 配合使用？</h3><p>目前，微软的 Xbox 游戏机不支持任何 VR 耳机。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-vr-headsets-140012529.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-vr-headsets-140012529.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 85ff34bf-f6f7-4878-80c1-5f155e7af14b</guid><dc:creator>德文德拉·哈达瓦尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 17:35:04 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692293704</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T17:35:11+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Devindra Hardawar]]></category><media:content height="1148" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-07/e35896d1-eb10-11eb-b7ff-c8fd80773144" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1148" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-07/e35896d1-eb10-11eb-b7ff-c8fd80773144" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Devindra Hardawar/Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[HTC Vive Pro 2]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[HTC Vive Pro 2]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Acura's ZDX EV has an estimated 325 miles of range and starts at around $60,000]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/honda/"><ins>本田</ins></a>希望在电动汽车市场掀起波澜。该汽车制造商 2024 年进军该领域的第一款车型是讴歌 ZDX。其基本 A-Spec 单电机配置预计一次充电可行驶 325 英里的 EPA 续航里程。</p><p>这与特斯拉 Model X（333 英里）大致相同，但优于 Model Y（303 英里），以及福特野马 Mach-E（长达 312 英里）和 F-150 Lightning（230 英里）。更重要的是，本田推出的该系列起价约为 60,000 美元。首批 Acura ZDX 预计于 2024 年初交付，并于今年晚些时候开始<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.acura.com/EarlyAccessZDX"><ins>预售</ins></a>。销售将<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/acuras-evs-will-be-sold-exclusively-online-starting-in-2024-140054959.html"><ins>仅在网上进行</ins></a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/acura-teases-the-zdx-its-first-electric-vehicle-130051990.html"><ins>在本月早些时候对这款电动汽车进行了预告</ins></a>后，在蒙特利汽车周上推出了这款电动汽车。它将有两种型号：Acura ZDX A-Spec 和 ZDX Type S。前者预计可提供 340 马力。双电机、全轮驱动 ZDX Type S 预计功率为 500 马力，起价约为 70,000 美元。本田表示，这将是“有史以来最强大、性能最好的讴歌 SUV”，但预计 102 kWh 电池的续航里程将缩短至 288 英里。值得注意的是，ZDX A-Spec 将配备 20 英寸车轮，而 Type S 则配备 22 英寸车轮。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/43e3ce60-3d13-11ee-bebf-9b8c615cb400" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/43e3ce60-3d13-11ee-bebf-9b8c615cb400" style="height:3113px;width:4670px;" alt="讴歌 ZDX S 型" data-uuid="73ba3f05-0338-3232-aa56-ea0bff80f6fa"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">马伦·洛</div></figure><p><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/acura-zdx-ev-gets-android-auto-and-built-in-google-apps-161232778.html"><ins>几个月来，本田一直在不断透露有关 ZDX 的详细信息</ins></a>，因此人们已经知道这款电动汽车将配备 Android Auto、内置谷歌应用程序和 Apple CarPlay 集成。它将配备一个 11 英寸的驾驶员触摸屏仪表板和一个 11.3 英寸的中央显示屏。 ZDX 是首款标配 Bang &amp; Olufsen 音响系统的 Acura 车型。它有 18 个扬声器，包括一个低音炮。</p><p>安全功能包括后行人警报和盲区转向辅助。 ZDX Type S 具有免提巡航驾驶员辅助功能。据 Acura 称，这可以“在兼容的道路上实现真正的免提驾驶，行驶里程可达 400,000 英里”。 Type S还配备了自动停车辅助系统，可以帮助平行停车。</p><p>在给电动汽车电池充电时，本田希望您永远不会距离充电站太远。上个月，它<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/major-automakers-team-up-to-create-new-north-american-ev-charging-network-171532385.html"><ins>宣布</ins></a>与其他六家汽车制造商共同努力，在北美建立一个由 30,000 个加油站组成的广泛网络。该计划的首批门店预计将于明年夏天在美国开业。本田还指出，ZDX 支持直流快速充电，在后轮驱动配置下，10 分钟充电即可为 ZDX A-Spec 的电池增加最多 81 英里的续航里程。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/61d92dc0-3d13-11ee-b7fd-23c037aaa7e5" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/61d92dc0-3d13-11ee-b7fd-23c037aaa7e5" style="height:3065px;width:4597px;" alt="讴歌 ZDX S 型" data-uuid="4ae81f49-4824-3ae5-a7a4-5f9c6f017aa6"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">马伦·洛</div></figure><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/acuras-zdx-ev-has-an-estimated-325-miles-of-range-and-starts-at-around-60000-160023372.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/acuras-zdx-ev-has-an-estimated-325-miles-of-range-and-starts-at-around-60000-160023372.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b539c00c-a350-4626-9049-31da0f0b5df9</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 17 Aug 2023 16:00:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692287121</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T15:45:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2684" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/2d3ab840-3d13-11ee-bcef-dab10f0e1c37" width="4024"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2684" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/2d3ab840-3d13-11ee-bcef-dab10f0e1c37" width="4024"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[MullenLowe]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Acura ZDX Type S]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Acura ZDX Type S]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[How to choose the best pizza oven in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>近年来，小型户外披萨烤箱已成为流行的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-fall-outdoor-tech-gear-150041103.html">后院</a>烹饪选择。虽然任何拥有足够大露台的人都可以安装永久性的产品，但这些多功能产品更加紧凑，并且在您不使用时可以轻松存放在包中。这使得这些便携式披萨烤箱非常适合室外空间有限的家庭厨师，并允许您根据需要携带它们上路。在室内拥有专用披萨烤箱也有不错的选择。以下是您在购买之前需要考虑的一些规格，以及我们精选的最佳披萨烤箱。</p><h2>要找什么</h2><p>在购买家用披萨烤箱时，您首先要考虑您打算制作什么类型的馅饼。 Ooni、Solo Stove 等公司的大多数便携式户外披萨烤箱都使用木材，主要设计用于轻薄通风的那不勒斯风格披萨所需的高温烹饪。我们谈论的是高达 900 华氏度的高温。 These units can certainly cook different styles at cooler temperatures, but they&#39;re easiest to use when you&#39;re running them wide open with a full load of wood.</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> You&#39;ll also want to consider alternate fuel types. If you purchase a propane or natural gas burner, you can adjust temperatures easily by turning a knob. For this reason, I recommend you spend the extra $100 or so on that accessory. This dual-fuel option makes your pizza oven a lot more versatile and gives you the option to still have a freshly fired pie when you don&#39;t feel like messing with wood or charcoal. If you only want to cook with gas, there are models available that only use propane or natural gas.</p><p> The other key consideration for aspiring pizza makers is size. Most companies make ovens that fit 12-inch pizzas, a perfect size for one person. They&#39;re also great for pizza parties, since people can customize their own without having to pick off toppings they don&#39;t like. If you want to make larger pizzas or plan to use your oven for other things (pans, etc), consider a larger version that can accommodate more than just small pies. The interior dimensions – or at the very least the pizza stone size – will be listed on most product pages. </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-04/5d227b90-d88e-11ed-abef-0e6778381ba5" alt="The best pizza ovens for 2023" data-uuid="6d884542-b842-38a2-b0ce-8f51a108a27e"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Photo by Billy Steele/Engadget</div></figure><h2> Plan for success</h2><p> Making quality pizza at home requires a considerable amount of counter or table space. You&#39;ll need room to stretch and prep your pizza dough, lay out your mozzarella, other cheeses and toppings and load pies onto a peel. Of course, some folks will be comfortable working in the tight confines of a small kitchen, but I&#39;ve found it much easier to use extra space to make sure I&#39;m not constantly moving things around during the various steps in the process.</p><p> It&#39;s also less hassle to set up your pizza-making station in close proximity to your oven. As a pizza-baking beginner, I did the running back and forth from the kitchen to the back porch. It&#39;s far from ideal. It&#39;s difficult to maintain your fire (if using wood or charcoal) when you&#39;re unable to watch it closely. The good news is a patio table can be easily converted into a pizza station with a large cutting board. This also gets your oven off the ground so it&#39;s easier to access.</p><p> Ooni <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Ooni Pizza Ovens;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0de15002-ec35-49d8-b24c-3d060213cd2b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Ooni+Pizza+Ovens&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIwZGUxNTAwMi1lYzM1LTQ5ZDgtYjI0Yy0zZDA2MDIxM2NkMmIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9vb25pLmNvbS9jb2xsZWN0aW9ucy9tb3JlIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJlNTgyZGU0Ny04NTUxLTQzODMtYmVhNy0xMTI4OWIxNDMyZTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVpCSPYvpwI5lfnVJUfzhd1ZlHNXKWc0Kq5RmAT8AHRu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fooni.com%2Fcollections%2Fmore">sells tables</a> for its ovens that also offer shelving and storage for peels and other accessories. Solo Stove has a <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Solo Stove;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f5421854-3d3e-46b7-ba38-db91920c7f00&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Solo+Stove&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJmNTQyMTg1NC0zZDNlLTQ2YjctYmEzOC1kYjkxOTIwYzdmMDAiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9zb2xvc3RvdmUuY29tL2VuLXVzL3AvcGktc3RhbmQiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImU1ODJkZTQ3LTg1NTEtNDM4My1iZWE3LTExMjg5YjE0MzJlOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUKHwEUykJvcI06_XD6oAcpNoanJJR--93u-mD8kpP85&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsolostove.com%2Fen-us%2Fp%2Fpi-stand">rolling stand</a> for its Pi oven too, with small side shelves and a spot for your propane tank underneath. Of course, you can find other tables and stands to suit your needs, just make sure they can withstand any heat that may radiate from the bottom of the oven while cooking. Most ovens are either well insulated or don&#39;t project too much excess heat toward the table, but you can never be too careful. For that reason, a stainless steel or metal surface is a good choice to set up an outdoor model.</p><p> Most of these ovens cook quickly at high heat, especially if you&#39;re making Neapolitan pizza. Having everything you need nearby so you can keep tabs on the oven and quickly make the next pizza will ease a lot of unnecessary headaches. When your cook time is two minutes or less, you don&#39;t want to venture too far.</p><h2> Best outdoor pizza ovens</h2><h3> A good multi-fuel outdoor pizza oven: Ooni Karu 16</h3><p><core-commerce id="8367926575a042b3b60489c470fbb6db" data-type="product-list"></p><p> If you&#39;re looking to go all-in on an outdoor pizza oven, you can&#39;t go wrong with <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdlmvMi7k25EJJDjFNPU2W_bx6VJqdXqxG1Z6YBHWKI6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOoni-Karu-Multi-Fuel-Outdoor-Pizza%2Fdp%2FB095CJ5KSD%2F">Ooni&#39;s Karu 16</a> . It&#39;s the company&#39;s largest multi-fuel model, which means you can choose between wood, charcoal or gas (propane and natural gas burners sold separately). This one is equipped with a hinged glass door for keeping tabs on your progress and a digital thermometer monitors the ambient temperature inside. The larger size means you can not only cook bigger pizzas, but the Karu 16 can also accommodate pans and cast iron, so baking, roasting and searing are all possible here. It&#39;s this versatility and ease of use that makes the Karu 16 our top pick.</p><h3> A solid outdoor pizza oven: Solo Stove Pi</h3><p><core-commerce id="3ae80c749a4346a185e2f54390f6106c" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Solo Stove may be on your radar for <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/solo-stoves-fire-pit-20-removable-base-plate-ash-pan-cleanup-143100211.html">its fire pits</a> , but the company also makes a <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARw-Do09kGbwfRdiZRKlaXkKuq5J7mbqweiatd-dPp5f&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSolo-Stove-Assembly-Cordierite-Stainless%2Fdp%2FB0B7XXXCZG%2F">solid multi-fuel pizza oven</a> . Dubbed the Pi, this unit is made out of stainless steel and is round like the company&#39;s trademark products. Solo Stove says Pi can hit cooking temperatures of 850 degrees Fahrenheit with wood and 900 degrees with a gas burner (sold separately). It explains that those figures translate to maximum stone temps of 750 and 800 degrees respectively. The Solo Stove Pi&#39;s big difference from the Karu 16 and other Ooni ovens is that it doesn&#39;t have a front door and stays open the whole time like a brick oven to allow more airflow.</p><h3> Small pizza oven option: Ooni Fyra 12</h3><p><core-commerce id="4c4c3bf387d84aacb46602119cc775cc" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASFRLfAzMLiznhxBXI5Wuh0iHp4OF_3dwFo9cR_xUWyZ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOoni-Fyra-Outdoor-Portable-Kitchen%2Fdp%2FB088385N9Z%2F">Ooni Fyra 12</a> was the first outdoor pizza oven I used and it remains one of my favorites. It&#39;s compact compared to some of the alternatives (22 pounds), so it won&#39;t take up quite as much storage space. It also runs on wood pellets instead of chunks, and once you get the fire going, you just refill the chute from the top. This means there&#39;s much less tending a fire on the Fyra than other wood-fired pizza ovens, so you can focus on making and cooking your pizzas. The Fyra does all the things other Ooni pizza ovens do well, including high-heat bakes (950 degrees) in as little as a minute.</p><h2> Indoor pizza ovens</h2><p> Let me preface this section by saying you probably already have an indoor option that you can use to make some great pizza. Whether that&#39;s the main oven in your kitchen or a multi-function countertop unit, with some affordable accessories, you can easily up your game without spending $1,000 on a dedicated appliance. For example, my <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVcylFxGokn8E7kN4RYhg0kXpXkUgvfVEyVbjXsQ9LQt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBreville-BOV860BSS-Countertop-Convection-Stainless%2Fdp%2FB085FTBLC6">Breville Smart Oven Air Fryer</a> has a convection pizza setting that automatically adjusts cook time based on the size, oven temperature and whether the pie is fresh or frozen. A key consideration here is size. These things are massive, about the size of a large microwave, so you likely won&#39;t want to keep them out all the time unless you have a huge kitchen.</p><h3> A versatile indoor pizza oven: Ooni Volt 12</h3><p><core-commerce id="33bf4ffb93984ec88bb89000fd3bc3b9" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Ooni made its name on outdoor pizza ovens that primarily burn wood or run on gas. For 2023, the company is taking things indoors with the <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Ooni Pizza Ovens;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0de15002-ec35-49d8-b24c-3d060213cd2b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Ooni+Pizza+Ovens&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIwZGUxNTAwMi1lYzM1LTQ5ZDgtYjI0Yy0zZDA2MDIxM2NkMmIiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9vb25pLmNvbS9wcm9kdWN0cy9vb25pLXZvbHQiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImU1ODJkZTQ3LTg1NTEtNDM4My1iZWE3LTExMjg5YjE0MzJlOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbs6K5UOSm8E-W_bMajznrC6hE6gSrwegRQG3GoG3gqs&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fooni.com%2Fproducts%2Fooni-volt">Volt 12</a> . <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/oonis-volt-12-is-the-companys-first-indoor-pizza-oven-173011466.html">Ooni&#39;s first electric oven</a> can also be used outside thanks to weather resistant construction, but this behemoth brings the company&#39;s design and efficiency to your kitchen for the first time. Capable of temperatures up to 850 degrees Fahrenheit in as little as 20 minutes, the Volt 12 can fire up Neapolitan style pies in 90 seconds. Controls on the front give you the ability to adjust both the top and bottom heating elements. There are also cooking presets and a Boost function to quickly get the stone back to temp between pizzas. The 13-inch stone inside is square, so you can slide in pans for Detroit recipes or other baked goods.</p><h3> A solid indoor pizza oven: Breville Pizzaiolo</h3><p><core-commerce id="c6f69080a1ba415c81d05f070daaf78e" data-type="product-list"></p><p> If you&#39;re set on buying a dedicated pizza oven, the <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9CcmV2aWxsZS1QaXp6YWlvbG8tQlBaODIwQlNTLUJydXNoZWQtU3RhaW5sZXNzL2RwL0IwOFI4WVpSMzI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tc3AtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImU1ODJkZTQ3LTg1NTEtNDM4My1iZWE3LTExMjg5YjE0MzJlOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZpOAEufnbwWCGDzjVUYurIRPrRyq2rE2abyRwwaeYbL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBreville-Pizzaiolo-BPZ820BSS-Brushed-Stainless%2Fdp%2FB08R8YZR32">Breville Pizzaiolo</a> is another great option, but it&#39;s just as pricey as the Volt 12. The Pizzaiolo cooks 12-inch pies as well, but the stone on this unit is perfectly sized for them and there&#39;s a metal heat reflector panel inside that will also keep you from overshooting the cooking surface. This means you won&#39;t be sliding larger rectangle pans in here like you can with the electric Ooni. Round pans fit just fine and some smaller square ones likely will too.</p><p> In terms of cooking ability, Breville offers presets for “Wood Fired,” New York, Pan, Thin &amp; Crispy and Frozen types of pizza with the added option to run the oven full blast at 750 degrees Fahrenheit. A second dial allows you to adjust the top heating element depending on how dark you want your pizza. Like it does on other Breville appliances, Element IQ tech adjusts the heating elements based on the selected style, creating the ideal environment for each one. For advanced users, the company offers a manual mode that turns the timer dial into a control for the bottom deck while the style preset selector manages the top. Breville includes a magnetic overlay for the front panel to show you temperatures for the converted controls. The instruction manual also gives you recommendations for where to begin with manual mode for the aforementioned styles.</p><h3> The best pizza accessories for the oven you already have</h3><p> If you want to make good homemade pizza that rivals that of your favorite pizzeria (and without spending hundreds of dollars on a dedicated oven), you can definitely do it with the oven you already have in your kitchen. With a few gadgets, you can improve your game without splurging on a Breville, Ooni or Solo Stove. First, I&#39;d recommend a high quality baking steel or stone.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAYhn2BEXBjIlUhVUE-gcCDCKkKEbWS800nVc0GwssboU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FOld-Stone-Oven-Rectangular-Pizza%2Fdp%2FB0000E1FDA%3Fref_%3Dast_sto_dp">Baking stones</a> are great for getting better browning on the bottom of your pies than a pizza or sheet pan. You can also use them for bread, cookies and other items. The stone absorbs heat to cook pizza quickly, like the inside of a brick oven, which leads to a charred crust. They&#39;re also more affordable compared to <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeEbDEKojEDMsFXyWihRBYfzEgwmrp2Q1uKdD4J5W_F7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBaking-Steel-Original-Ultra-Conductive%2Fdp%2FB00N205G22%3F">baking steels</a> . Those metal slabs do have one key advantage: higher heat conductivity. This means a steel will cook your pizzas faster since it can absorb more heat from your oven. While baking steels can be used as griddles on your stovetop and for other types of baking, they&#39;re not ideal for some leavened breads.</p><p> The second item you&#39;ll want is a <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9OZXctU3Rhci1Gb29kc2VydmljZS01MDI5NS1Xb29kZW4vZHAvQjAwOUxQRE5QTy8_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tc3AtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImU1ODJkZTQ3LTg1NTEtNDM4My1iZWE3LTExMjg5YjE0MzJlOCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAeHLwzq7fJFIm1-ixj3_YAjMRj60G1dLxlCwHW3rnnFH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNew-Star-Foodservice-50295-Wooden%2Fdp%2FB009LPDNPO%2F">pizza peel</a> . These come in all shapes and sizes, made out of a variety of materials. I typically use a bamboo or wooden peel when topping and launching my pizzas and then a metal one for retrieving them. I&#39;ve found that dough doesn&#39;t stick as easily to bamboo during prep and the metal resists the high heat of the oven when turning or retrieving a finished pizza (bamboo will burn). There are also <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDdUNVMyTERELz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby1zcC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZTU4MmRlNDctODU1MS00MzgzLWJlYTctMTEyODliMTQzMmU4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAdpQInLNp63_vvTnwW6Llpp877uFvnQmCfWr57mSHCYX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07T5S2LDD%2F">perforated peels</a> which allow both steam and excess flour to escape. A peel is a great tool for loading and turning pizzas, getting them in the back of the oven, and since you&#39;ll typically be cooking them with your oven at 500 degrees or hotter, using something like parchment paper to move them around won&#39;t work.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-pizza-oven-141550352.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-pizza-oven-141550352.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e582de47-8551-4383-bea7-11289b1432e8</guid><dc:creator> Billy Steele</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 17 Aug 2023 15:20:47 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692285648</ingested><modified> 2023-08-17T15:20:57+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Commodity Markets]]></category><category><![CDATA[Home & Garden]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Billy Steele]]></category><media:content height="13